/***********************************************************************
********** PROGRAM NAME: ZPe - PE Reader - *****************************
********** Essay:
********** This software allows to analyze and logs lot of usefull
********** informations from any PE file, such as EXEs and DLLs.
********** 
********** Skills:
**********				- Logs PE's header informations
**********				- Logs API and functions imported by the file
**********				- Logs function exported by the file (if any)
**********            - Allows to add a new section into the file
**********
********** In the next versions:
**********				- Hex viewer and editor
**********				- Protections/packers scanner and identifier
